A selection of open-mic regulars from the music and arts community Artifex and a few of our partners.  Join us at Punchline Comedy’s club as musical talents from Artifex, Midnight Melodies, and Nyx Entertainment put their passion on display!  And for the punchline at the end of this set up, a skit from the Punchline crew themselves!

Join us over on discord at discord.gg/artifex.  We are always happy to make new friends!
